<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>523</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ gào sù wǒ, tóu shàng xiǎng gāo yóu duō, tiān tiān bèi qǐ shí zì jià, guò shèng jié shēng huó.
 zhǔ gào sù wǒ, tóu shàng xiǎng gāo yóu duō, xīn xiōng kuān guǎng ài chóu dí, cháng sī zì jǐ guò.
 tóu shàng xiǎng gāo yóu duō, shén me dōu bù quē, róng shén yì rén duō bēn bō, fán shì dōu wèi zhǔ zuò,
 fēn fēn miǎo miǎo guò, rì chū yòu rì luò, zhǔ gào sù wǒ xiǎng gāo yóu duō, dé guò shèng jié shēng huó.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ gào sù wǒ 迦南523</title>
</song>